# wandb artifact cache

## 

​

Usage
    
    
    cache [OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...
    

## 

​

Description

Manage the local artifact cache. Cache downloaded artifact files locally to avoid redundant downloads. Use subcommands to inspect and reclaim disk space used by the cache.

## 

​

Subcommands

Command| Description  
---|---  
`wandb artifact cache cleanup`| Reduce the local artifact cache size.  
  
